{"word":"ἀληθῶς","slug":"ἀληθῶς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀληϑῶς</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀληθής\">ἀληθής</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> ‘corresponding to what is really so’, <b><i>truly, really, actually</i> <a href='B:470 14:33'>Mt 14:33</a>; <a href='B:480 14:70'>Mk 14:70</a>; <a href='B:490 9:27'>Lk 9:27</a>; <a href='B:500 7:26'>J 7:26</a>; <a href='B:500 8:31'>8:31</a></b> of real disciples, not merely so in name; <b><a href='B:510 12:11'>Ac 12:11</a>; <a href='B:590 2:13'>1 Th 2:13</a>; <a href='B:690 2:5'>1 J 2:5</a>.</b> Of Nathanael: <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀληθῶς\">ἀληθῶς</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:Ἰσραηλίτης\">Ἰσραηλίτης</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a> ᾧ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δόλος\">δόλος</a> <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οὐκ\">οὐκ</a> ἔστιν</el> <i>no doubt about it, an Israelite without deceit</i> <b><a href='B:500 1:47'>J 1:47</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀλήθω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἁλιεύς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}